g.text: Heres a quick tour of the project:
A FastAPI starter template with modern patterns and dependency injection, built around a
3-layer architecture. It includes auth, user management, admin UI, Swagger protection, and
- ORM: SQLAlchemy 2 (async) + Alembic migrations; MySQL 8.0+ via `aiomysql`
- `api.py`: Main FastAPI app; wires dependency containers, sets up CORS, sessions, admin,
routes, exception handler. Swagger is moved to `/docs/openapi.json` and UI locked to
- `auth/`: JWT auth endpoints, schemas, service, exceptions.
- `user/`: User endpoints, repository, service, admin registration.
